<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hungtei Ding</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa Aw-gi chu ngaitiem u,
 Leisiet a mite'n;
 A hungna ding ni anai tai,
 I sepgah kimlo.

[V2]
 Hungtei dingin (2)
 Van thamzawl mei chung ah;
 Lopi takin hung kipuong ina.

[V3]
 2. Aman atel chuomte a puih,
 Toh ni tieng chu leh;
 A nutsiehte haw cheng vang chu'n,
 Gimtheih thuok tan au.

[V4]
 3. Gawtmun meidil aumte chun,
 Kum sang sawm-sang za;
 Lunggimtheihna thuok kumkhuo ding,
 Hin ding guo mah leu;

[V5]
 4. Van goluoh ding chengte vang chu,
 Vak sing seng un au;
 Pa lungkim na um theilo ding,
 I sepgah kimlo.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>326</hymn_number>
</song>